07:52.515 --> 07:55.126
-DON'T BLAME ME,
DARLING, I DIDN'T DO IT.

07:55.257 --> 07:56.693
-IT CAN MAKE YOU SICK.

07:56.824 --> 07:58.347
-I DON'T WANT TO GET SICK.

07:58.478 --> 08:00.218
-COME ON, ERNIE, BE A GOOD GUY.

08:00.349 --> 08:02.220
